      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must be verified under a documented quality management system with version control and regression testing.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent v19.2 used under ISO 9001-compliant QMS. Version control and regression test suite documented. Achieved level meets required level for MRL 2."
    },
    {
