      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must pass standard benchmark verification cases relevant to rotating machinery and viscous flow.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent has been verified against lid-driven cavity, Taylor-Couette flow, and rotating disk benchmarks. Published verification reports confirm second-order spatial accuracy."
