      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted relative hemolysis index (RH) must agree with experimental measurements within 15% across all five operating points.",
      "rationale": "Predicted RH values ranged from 0.71 to 0.94 across operating points. Mean absolute error versus experimental data was 8.3%. All predictions fell within the 15% acceptance band. Worst-case operating condition correctly identified at 6 L/min, 3500 RPM."
