    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors achieved the required level for MRL 2. Six factors were appropriately scoped as not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements for a Class II device. The CFD model correctly identifies worst-case hemolysis operating conditions with RH predictions within 15% of experimental data across all five operating points. The relative hemolysis index remains below 1.0 at all conditions, satisfying the regulatory acceptance criterion. The credibility evidence package is accepted as sufficient to support the intended regulatory submission.",
